</section>

<!-- "Why You Shouldn't Use RTMX" - Reverse Psychology Section -->
<section class="dont-use-section" id="dont-use">
  <h2><span class="strikethrough">DON'T</span> Use RTMX</h2>
  <p class="dont-use-intro">Seriously. It's not for everyone. Here's why you should probably stay away:</p>

  <div class="dont-use-grid">
    <div class="dont-use-card">
      <h3>You already have a spreadsheet.</h3>
      <p>
        And you definitely don't spend 2 hours every sprint reconciling it with what actually shipped.
        That's just part of the process, right?
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="dont-use-card">
      <h3>AI-generated code always works.</h3>
      <p>
        Your agent never confidently implements the wrong feature or quietly breaks something three files away.
        No need to trace what it changed back to what you actually asked for.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="dont-use-card">
      <h3>You love Jira.</h3>
      <p>
        RTMX is distributed and version-controlled with your code. Way worse than managing requirements
        in a GUI that's definitely not loading right now.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="dont-use-card">
      <h3>You don't want to pay $9.</h3>
      <p>
        You'd rather spend 9 hours every week fixing the tech debt slop that AI creates for your team.
        Time is money, but it's <em>your</em> time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="dont-use-card">
      <h3>Tests prove nothing.</h3>
      <p>
        You trust your test suite, even if nobody can remember which features it actually covers.
        "I think auth is tested somewhere" is basically the same as traceability.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="dont-use-card">
      <h3>Dependencies are obvious.</h3>
      <p>
        Your team instinctively knows that REQ-47 blocks REQ-12 which blocks REQ-89.
        Why would you need a graph for that?
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="dont-use-card">
      <h3>Your AI knows the codebase.</h3>
      <p>
        Context windows are unlimited now. Your agent never forgets the requirement
        it was working on or what tests need to pass. Refresh the chat? No problem.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="dont-use-card">
      <h3>Audits are fine.</h3>
      <p>
        "Show me every requirement and its test" is a reasonable ask and you can answer it in 5 minutes.
        You've definitely done the drill and it went great.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="still-reading">
    <p><strong>Still reading?</strong> Sounds like you might actually need RTMX.</p>
    <a href="/quickstart" class="hero-button primary">Get Started</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <p>
    Built by <a href="https://iotactical.co">ioTACTICAL Engineering</a> |
    <a href="mailto:dev@rtmx.ai">dev@rtmx.ai</a>
  </p>
</footer>

<style is:global>
  /* Hide Starlight's default hero/title on homepage */
  .hero,
  main > header,
  .content-panel > header,
  [aria-label="Main"] > header,
  .main-pane > h1:first-child,
  .sl-markdown-content > h1:first-child {
    display: none !important;
  }
</style>

<style>
  /* Hero Header - Title at very top */
  .hero-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #0f0f0f 100%);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #6ee7b7 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #9ca3af;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 850px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .hero-button.primary {
    background: #10b981;
    color: #0a0a0a;
  }

  .hero-button.primary:hover {
    background: #6ee7b7;
  }

  .hero-button.secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: #10b981;
    border: 2px solid #10b981;
  }

  .hero-button.secondary:hover {
    background: #10b981;
    color: #0a0a0a;
  }

  .github-button {
    background: #10b981;
    color: #0a0a0a;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
  }

  .github-button:hover {
    background: #6ee7b7;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
  }

  /* Hero Illustration - Full width */
  .hero-illustration-section {
    width: 100%;
    background: #0f0f0f;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-illustration-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-illustration-container img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  /* Feature Grid */
  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #0f0f0f;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: #171717;
    border: 1px solid #262626;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: #10b981;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    color: #f9fafb;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .feature-card code {
    background: #262626;
    color: #e5e7eb;
    padding: 0.15em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 0.85em;
  }

  .feature-card.coming-soon {
    position: relative;
    border-color: #f59e0b40;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .feature-card.coming-soon h3,
  .feature-card.coming-soon p {
    width: 100%;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .feature-card.coming-soon:hover {
    border-color: #f59e0b;
  }

  .feature-card .badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
    color: #0a0a0a;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* Statistics Section */
  .stats-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #0a0a0a;
    border-top: 1px solid #262626;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #262626;
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .stat-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #6ee7b7 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .stat-label {
    display: block;
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .stat-card a {
    display: inline-block;
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .stat-card a:hover {
    color: #10b981;
  }

  /* Comparison Section */
  .comparison-section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: #0a0a0a;
  }

  .comparison-section h2 {
    color: #f9fafb;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .comparison-subtitle {
    color: #9ca3af;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .table-wrapper {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .comparison-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    background: #171717;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    table-layout: fixed;
  }

  .comparison-table th,
  .comparison-table td {
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #262626;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .comparison-table th:first-child,
  .comparison-table td:first-child {
    text-align: left;
    width: 25%;
  }

  .comparison-table th:not(:first-child),
  .comparison-table td:not(:first-child) {
    width: 15%;
  }

  .comparison-table th {
    background: #0f0f0f;
    color: #f9fafb;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .comparison-table td {
    color: #d1d5db;
  }

  .comparison-table .check {
    color: #22c55e;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .comparison-table .cross {
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  .comparison-table .partial {
    color: #f59e0b;
  }

  .comparison-table .coming-soon {
    color: #f59e0b;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .site-footer {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid #262626;
    background: #0a0a0a;
  }

  .site-footer p {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .site-footer a {
    color: #10b981;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .site-footer a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* "DON'T Use RTMX" Section */
  .dont-use-section {
    background: #070707;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #262626;
  }

  .dont-use-section h2 {
    color: #f9fafb;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .dont-use-section h2 .strikethrough {
    text-decoration: line-through;
    text-decoration-color: #ef4444;
    text-decoration-thickness: 3px;
  }

  .dont-use-intro {
    color: #9ca3af;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .dont-use-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .dont-use-card {
    background: #0d0d0d;
    border: 1px solid #1f1f1f;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .dont-use-card h3 {
    color: #f3f4f6;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .dont-use-card p {
    color: #b8bfc9;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .dont-use-card code {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #9ca3af;
    padding: 0.15em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 0.85em;
  }

  .dont-use-card em {
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .still-reading {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #1f1f1f;
  }

  .still-reading p {
    color: #d1d5db;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .still-reading .hero-button.primary {
    background: #10b981;
    color: #0a0a0a;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .still-reading .hero-button.primary:hover {
    background: #6ee7b7;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .feature-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .stats-section {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-header {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .stats-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .feature-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .comparison-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .comparison-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .comparison-table {
      table-layout: auto;
    }

    .comparison-table th,
    .comparison-table td {
      padding: 0.75rem 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .comparison-table th:first-child,
    .comparison-table td:first-child {
      width: auto;
    }

    .comparison-table th:not(:first-child),
    .comparison-table td:not(:first-child) {
      width: auto;
    }

    .dont-use-section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .dont-use-section h2 {
